    "rowsha": "qwJ0dhua1ypoog+04KOpi0MIHXbME2HMudcS6nVugtQ=",
    "originContent": "I highly recommend using flatpak version, because, distro based wine (wine-staging) keeps on updating and games may break every few days. Using wine stable from flathub is better or use wine stable 5.0 or 7.0 from the distro packages.",
    "translatedContent": "Je recommande fortement d'utiliser la version flatpak, car la version wine des distributions (wine-staging) est fréquemment mise à jour et les jeux peuvent cesser de fonctionner tous les quelques jours. Utiliser wine stable de flathub est préférable ou bien wine stable 5.0 ou 7.0 des paquets de la distribution."
